OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FTurning
OL,6,Fgradually cloudier through the evening
OL,7,Fand into the night with outbreaks of
OL,8,Frain spreading east from dusk. Rain
OL,9,Fpersisting overnight with some heavier
OL,10,Fbursts possible over the moors.
OL,11,FTurning increasingly blustery.
OL,12,
OL,13,CFriday:FBlustery, cloudy and damp with
OL,14,Flight rain and drizzly outbreaks
OL,15,Fpossible for much of the day. Low
OL,16,Fcloud and misty conditions likely
OL,17,Facross high ground and in coastal
OL,18,Fareas.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
