OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FWindy
OL,6,Fwith scattered showers Saturday,
OL,7,Fperhaps some longer spells of rain
OL,8,Fovernight. Bright and breezy on Easter
OL,9,FSunday, with scattered showers. Winds
OL,10,Feasing leaving a drier and warmer
OL,11,FEaster Monday.
